This a review of Viz Media's treatment of the series as an available product of the series in the states, rather than this specific item. Aren't we tired of seeing these collections at a huge price for the amount of episodes we get? Stop purchasing these and maybe VIZ will finally release a viable product that includes at least fifty episodes.

I bought this box set because I have all of the previous box sets of the Series. This box set isn't as interesting as the previous two, most of the box set is about Naruto heading to the Land of Lightning by boat & all of the episodes are telling what happens to Naruto on his way to his destination. Some of the episodes aren't bad but they're still kind of weird, it reminds me of the old days with the original Series of Naruto.
